metadata.name: Lovers
metadata.description:
At first, the government and society did not accept romances between humans, machines and neo-humans. But now, such relationships are becoming more common thanks to new laws implemented by the high council.

However, among the more conservative sectors, these relationships are still forbidden, so couples often meet in secret.
